<l>pīlipey cākāṭu macciṟu mappaṇṭañ</l>
<l>cāla mikuttup peyiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The axle tree of a bandy, loaded only with peacocks" feathers will break, if it be greatly overloaded.</l>
